---
---

<!-- Tip Info Box Section -->
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pt-4 pb-8 mb-4">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto relative bg-white pos-relative rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200 p-6 sm:p-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 lg:gap-8 items-start hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition-all duration-300 group">
    
    <!-- Lightbulb Icon Container -->
    <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-16 h-16 bg-red-50 text-autosport-red rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center border border-red-50 group-hover:bg-autosport-red group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 18v-5.25m0 0a6.01 6.01 0 001.5-.189m-1.5.189a6.01 6.01 0 01-1.5-.189m3.75 7.478a12.06 12.06 0 01-4.5 0m3.75 2.383a14.406 14.406 0 01-3 0M14.25 18v-.192c0-.983.658-1.82 1.508-2.316a7.5 7.5 0 10-7.517 0c.85.496 1.509 1.333 1.509 2.316V18" />
      </svg>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="flex-1">
      <!-- Badge -->
      <div class="mb-4">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide bg-slate-50 text-autosport-navy shadow-sm border border-slate-200 uppercase">
          <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 mr-1.5 text-autosport-red" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
          </svg>
          Informație utilă pentru cursanți
        </span>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Title & Description -->
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-autosport-navy mb-3 block">Știai că?</h3>
      <p class="text-slate-600 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Conform legislației în vigoare, în anumite situații nu mai este necesar examenul teoretic („sala”), ci doar proba practică (traseul).
      </p>

      <!-- Examples List -->
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-autosport-red mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-slate-700 leading-snug">Dacă deții <strong class="text-autosport-navy text-sm">categoria B</strong> și dorești <strong class="text-autosport-navy text-sm">A2 sau A</strong>, susții doar <strong class="text-autosport-navy text-sm">proba practică (traseul)</strong>.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-autosport-red mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-slate-700 leading-snug">Dacă deții <strong class="text-autosport-navy text-sm">A1</strong> și dorești <strong class="text-autosport-navy text-sm">A2 sau A</strong>, susții doar <strong class="text-autosport-navy text-sm">proba practică</strong> dacă ai minimum 2 ani experiență cu categoria A1.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-autosport-red mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
          <span class="text-slate-700 leading-snug">Dacă deții <strong class="text-autosport-navy text-sm">B1</strong> și dorești <strong class="text-autosport-navy text-sm">categoria B</strong>, susții doar <strong class="text-autosport-navy text-sm">proba practică</strong>.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="pt-4 border-t border-slate-100">
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 flex items-center font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2 text-autosport-red/70" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
             <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
          Pentru detalii complete despre situația ta, te putem consilia la înscriere.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
